{"tid":827742,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(HEHE芝麻街): 布偶畢特和恩尼是同性戀伴侶","createTime":"2018-09-19T07:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T12:57:35.000Z","uid":102732,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"393dd94882de68f70199eafeb24ca3830302548e","tid":827742,"uid":102732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:07:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%A8%E5%8A%87-%E5%B8%83%E5%81%B6%E7%95%A2%E7%89%B9%E5%92%8C%E6%81%A9%E5%B0%BC%E6%98%AF%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E4%BC%B4%E4%BE%B6-%E8%8A%9D%E9%BA%BB%E8%A1%97%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D-055004601.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E5%258A%2587-%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%2581%25B6%25E7%2595%25A2%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%2581%25A9%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2588%2580%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E4%25BE%25B6-%25E8%258A%259D%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D-055004601.html&d=vWTFKYeVB2iqjjbcuzELvI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8655f38e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%A8%E5%8A%87-%E5%B8%83%E5%81%B6%E7%95%A2%E7%89%B9%E5%92%8C%E6%81%A9%E5%B0%BC%E6%98%AF%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E4%BC%B4%E4%BE%B6-%E8%8A%9D%E9%BA%BB%E8%A1%97%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D-055004601.html</a><br />\n<br />\n（法新社紐約18日電） 長久以來觀眾對美國 長壽兒童電視節目芝麻街（Sesame Street）的布偶人 物畢特和恩尼的關係感到好奇，認為他們不只是麻吉室 友而已，芝麻街前編劇也出面證實他們是同性戀伴侶。 1981到 1990年擔任芝麻街節目編劇的薩茲曼（Mark Saltzman ）今天向同性戀權益相關資訊網站Queerty證實，畢特 （Bert）和恩尼（Ernie）是「親密伴侶」。 他並表示，他是根據他與電影剪輯師葛萊斯曼（ Arnold Glassman）長久的關係，寫出畢特和恩尼的互 動，但芝麻街創作團隊則否認他們在一起，也沒有性傾 向。（譯者：陳昱婷/核稿：張曉雯）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/29G.gGZtulLulSim014rqw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzY4O2g9NDk4O2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/afp/top0002b.180919135004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F29G.gGZtulLulSim014rqw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ